BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 728.5041732283464171 Td
(You are being invited to take part in a research study. Before you decide whether to participate, it is important) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 715.7482677165354517 Td
(for you to understand why the research is being done and what it will involve. Please take time to read the) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 702.9923622047243725 Td
