ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 681.7325196850392786 Td
(The purpose of this study \(Protocol VLX-4070-001\) is to evaluate the safety, tolerability, and) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 668.9766141732283131 Td
(pharmacokinetics of an investigational drug called Velanexor \(VLX-4070\) in patients with advanced cancers) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 656.2207086614173477 Td
(that have a specific genetic change called KRAS G12C. VLX-4070 is a selective allosteric inhibitor of kras) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 643.4648031496062686 Td
(g12c and has not been previously studied in humans. This is a "first-in-human" study.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 622.2049606299212883 Td
(Approximately 68 patients at multiple study centers will take part in this study. The study is sponsored by) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 609.4490551181102092 Td
(Velantis Therapeutics, Inc..) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 14 Tf
16.0999999999999979 TL
0.102 0.212 0.365 rg
56.6929133858267775 571.1813385826771992 Td
(2  2. Risks and Benefits) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 548.5041732283464171 Td
(Based on studies in laboratory animals, VLX-4070 may cause the following side effects: liver enzyme) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 535.748267716535338 Td
(elevations \(increased ALT and AST\), gastrointestinal symptoms \(nausea, vomiting, diarrhea\), fatigue, skin) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 522.9923622047243725 Td
(rash, and changes in heart rhythm \(QTc prolongation\). Some of these effects may be serious.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 501.7325196850393354 Td
(There may be risks that are not yet known. Because this drug has not been given to humans before,) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 488.9766141732283131 Td
(unexpected side effects may occur. Your study doctor will monitor you closely for any side effects throughout) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 476.2207086614172908 Td
(the study.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 454.9608661417322537 Td
(There is no guarantee that you will benefit directly from participating in this study. However, the information) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 442.2049606299212314 Td
(learned from this study may help future patients with similar cancers. If VLX-4070 is effective against your) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
11.5 TL
0.118 g
56.6929133858267775 429.4490551181101523 Td
(cancer, you may experience tumor shrinkage or stabilization of your disease.) Tj
ET
